      • getMessage

        public String getMessage​(Locale locale)
        Description copied from interface: ValidationResult
        This method gets the message localized for the given Locale.
        ATTENTION:
        This method is designed for server applications with NLS. On client side (e.g. in the web browser) only a single locale may be supported at a time and this method will behave like ValidationResult.getMessage() ignoring the Locale.
        Parameters:
        locale - is the Locale.
        Returns:
        the message.
